<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    /* General reset & body */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #0a1f11;
      color: #d5e8d4;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* Header styling */
    header {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #50c878;
      color: #0a1f11;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(80, 200, 120, 0.5);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* Main section */
    main {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    /* Intro section */
    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #143820;
      padding: 30px 25px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(80, 200, 120, 0.4);
    }

    .intro-img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(80, 200, 120, 0.3);
    }

    .intro h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #50c878;
    }

    .intro p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #c6e2c6;
    }

    /* Button */
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #50c878;
      color: #0a1f11;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(80, 200, 120, 0.5);
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #3aa35b;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(58, 163, 91, 0.7);
      color: #e6f1e6;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .intro {
        padding: 20px 15px;
      }

      .intro h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .intro p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>Welcome to the MFC Monitoring Dashboard</header>
  <main>
    <section class="intro">
      <img src="../public/image.jpg" alt="MFC System Diagram" class="intro-img">
      <h2>Monitor Real-Time Sensor Data from Your MFC System</h2>
      <p>
        The Microbial Fuel Cell (MFC) technology harnesses the power of bacteria to
        convert organic waste into clean electricity. This dashboard provides live
        data from sensors embedded in your MFC setup, helping you optimize performance,
        track environmental parameters, and ensure sustainable energy generation.
      </p>
      <p>
        By monitoring parameters such as voltage, current, pH levels, and temperature,
        you can detect changes and troubleshoot issues in real-time, maximizing
        efficiency and extending the lifespan of your MFC system.
      </p>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn">Go to Dashboard â†’</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
